{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "One post. Seven days. And the dev internet went to war.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9381edded443d871deb0ea2f2fbe654f8d3b4e663e4e248804be0f90b938ff05",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Eight days ago, an engineer at Anthropic dropped a thesis.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2a7985fc55eb37a244e760a627692c61d3a2080f804aebca7e2fa49587821841",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Markdown is the wrong format. For every spec.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7f7afa491bbd065e45069aa20e739cea8fdeb608df22b415786bc4ea73acb225",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 21
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Every plan. Every P R writeup. Almost all of it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2803def3d3fafe995306c9319ac6b5332c1e1fe834a314a821e94866346b8851",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 29
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Out. Seven hundred and fifty thousand views.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d60f835de79a8b4973b65ca893366829e69eefa9cc5977b4a1155d7895f455f8",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 39
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Two thousand seven hundred likes. Three hundred and forty reposts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cd3daddf1a55b26d9641118eebabc216d3237550527569de2a49e6b7e97197c5",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "That was day one. By day three, the Markdown camp came out swinging.",
      "checksum": "sha256:040c64e2fbb1dbc12d55601312a6f18b2748e433e95c64405ab37f80c9377462",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 56
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "By day five, the hybrid camp landed in the middle.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6880be73f0c9d4a7ad296770629eefbef9d0977f3565d252b84e56fc1a44631c",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 69
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "By day seven, the conspiracy camp pointed at the tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6f859a74d9b7ec23bb11c7859d97ff5ac05e04eee51fce506a2b622ce0bb9aba",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 79
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "And four days ago, the same engineer doubled down.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a897306d322b890d663da7b801f12717dfc609a43a4393c6abde6499d6c76a64",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 89
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "H T M L continues to be undefeated.\n\nThis is the debate that is still going.",
      "checksum": "sha256:97f3dd0dca710d96687776193b68f8821c94cb76efc4fdc576caf65093fcb40a",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 98
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "The pros. The cons. The receipts. And the question every team is going to have to answer themselves.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e4101b3c829847684191bc982e242fc975aa820066a13715b2b1f01937b19317",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 7.058866213151927,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 114
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "First \u2014 the case for H T M L. Thariq's original list.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cdc64a300fb9c45ce613b390a0fba004b6cf734365c652656bf6227c96e5a016",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 132
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Information density. Markdown can carry headings, bold, bullets, and a table if you squint at it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:381b544da0a094e8ae4c6dab28b9624fba6a1cd678dd4e35167b13dea3e736f4",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 5.804988662131519,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 144
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "H T M L can carry eight things in one file.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9ef89744f04bef22ae838c1c08aef87e29e49229d8dad3660097d31c0bfd939b",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 160
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Tables. C S S design. S V G illustrations.",
      "checksum": "sha256:770cf186ed79600e0c9707fe60c3850b9afbfbd0a9701223c828d12a17ed2140",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 171
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Code snippets inside script tags. Interactions wired with JavaScript.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c805d6dbb2653220db735814538a8664e160ae8e10687911bbea4f27b66a8801",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 180
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Workflows drawn side by side. Spatial data on a canvas.",
      "checksum": "sha256:20486d686835d02b641fa10b39086722ad015f9cb0c3113178ed18a82f6422b9",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 189
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "And actual images. The argument \u2014 there is almost nothing Claude can read that you cannot represent in H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:719dc5f4daac8623d0d9d05cd165e613dc63ff3494197d3bd8cee01d71f971ce",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 7.1053061224489795,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 199
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "A second engineer, on X, put it this way.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c44e829f70a8e324b8d2727eb6249c0f1b1f5f97b47eb83638620c694defd308",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 221
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "H T M L gives agents a richer canvas than Markdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:105ed21f0fb58007c559efe0ffab9dc3fcf78e2abd16a78c4ae4e7987d538340",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 230
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Diagrams, styling, layout, tables, S V Gs, images, and interactive elements.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fabb94922dfa4b2caeaf739e5d1f7fe44465d8ebd59d787043db0221cdd06be2",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 241
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "And the human in the loop. Instead of reviewing walls of text, you inspect, tweak, annotate, move sliders, copy changes back into prompts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b9bd04ae2479154b2d6015411a9f6a348022f5265933746975770afded3a9197",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 9.287981859410431,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 252
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "That is the steel-manned version of the H T M L side.",
      "checksum": "sha256:41eb8785a1530a94473940d5917dabe4c50a7a35bccfd6108e2aeb7d43c7f257",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 275
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Information goes in. A working interface comes out.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cc474e196b05c50e11b5cc60c9744b3de204c5c0320c7f10f62003de98c7470c",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 287
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "The viewer is back in the loop. Now the case for Markdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5869e4ad198c7e8824a1475a4590a5a0cdb3f34fe93ef079f25a8c4700cf0b3b",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 295
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Which is louder than you might expect. One comment, three hundred and sixty-nine likes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f673bc91c9df041e782b67050c1858d3c91b19f564d9303d904d8e22a4535988",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 5.154829931972789,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 307
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Simplicity is the feature, not a bug. Another, one hundred and forty-nine likes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:63a022bba9c507be6f3404a236139703e666882137dd87aaea5faa0f6cfdfcea",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 321
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Markdown already supports H T M L totally.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f3be09621df96f37e8d58c8722db37822da5932be57b4446cda969ec7cbc26b6",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 334
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Just put H T M L into your markdown when you need it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1792a2f90c08ae79f975b64b491288c3d1f9444ab8cf89a83db7c2f1d4276ac2",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 342
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Another, ninety-seven likes. M D saves so much tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b06c8b44965fe2dc9a692de95a5d77f2a277c63f98a43ad9111af67f36014990",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 355
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "All the time. Not some times. Another, fifty-nine likes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f22704600e8c195ea152bf2cce0df2f94cb14ac6eb2e19828d04bd9f62488703",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 364
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "Since when does markdown not have tables?",
      "checksum": "sha256:a13eb4ac41f15e8fe78162756e63c428daf7541a407d0074efc9a7d85fde3579",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 373
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "M D can be themed by editor previews. M D can be understood by non-technical people.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8285542be080506404c4c21299212bc664c424335827ea78d50630715525d7f7",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 380
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "So many pros over H T M L. And the strongest one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:abaf4fb0187d90b561b1b18180ac1f7870617876428816fe9ce64b0d8c9741df",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 396
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "Markdown is not a competitor to H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:882be2ae4542244edd1bd46f392cf15e0b4381a1bfceb0e800eb8b810b9bd21f",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 408
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "Markdown was literally designed to compile to H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3c75761a40056ce1c59fc221b4875fb82d32c5ebdd25663011b87c6733932f51",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 418
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "They are not opposing formats. One is the source.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e560a6f2a59570c56cec7735e5dcbe5bb5e1d280658f40b5b45db4bffb239d82",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 429
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "The other is the rendered artifact. The pushback is structural.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0dd8b61960b57fc9b777ee8eadc7e9d6dd0196c503578627acb4800464b609e2",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 438
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "Markdown is small. Markdown is portable.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f5e842799285fd4f4841b2364aae24d495f8e84f8970877b98f9ac0daeb832df",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 448
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Markdown is editable without tools. Markdown can already do tables, Mermaid diagrams, embedded images, S V G, and inline H T M L when you actually need it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:34501a527a448e926794dd76adea27130e71d0f49788afb4145bbffef688b62d",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 10.866938775510205,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 454
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "If you can do all of that in markdown, the question becomes \u2014 what is H T M L actually buying you?",
      "checksum": "sha256:074fce726a5add2063e8e58450527c7a64c136632b87076d25b0d3c85fbcf6da",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 7.523265306122449,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 482
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "Here are the receipts. From people who have actually measured it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6ec6bcef47b21f99f9d53d62095a9276dfef59f93a5779462ee17713911dc4e5",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 504
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "One engineer, on X. Twenty-five thousand tokens to generate one H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e28a3567dc1cd422b59ac35d35a147077820cff9ced27c120ddd6936e207e9ef",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 515
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "One thousand tokens for the same content in markdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f33d7cf630b0e17887f1e944137b7988e4a2037c334ac955eb54652799d2602a",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 529
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "Twenty-five times more tokens. Per artifact.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fcc1be49fa7c00674765944f7d8aece741fc28fd6cb4f94ea730d91778be84b1",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 538
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Another, on YouTube. Creating an H T M L explainer eats fifty percent of the five hour limit on Opus four point seven.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2e622fd60ae618e1b4d772278c55c310d69ec1f9abe104f8af2d16c7c37767b7",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 6.873106575963718,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 544
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "The pro-H T M L side has its own number.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d967b58caf67ddb7da92c8ec7d14054c8114bfa9dc929681450ffc3b573c8879",
      "wav": "chunk-47.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 567
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "Opus four point seven ships with a one million token context window.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a37875cd845026403dce32e40f80cdb3599e189f67e2f52fb97834239c99739d",
      "wav": "chunk-48.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 577
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "So the extra tokens, in absolute terms, fit.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fe3db35941e531263defc9e988636a7969bb145e4734d23bfc024a597d1fd23a",
      "wav": "chunk-49.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 589
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "text": "But here is the catch the community keeps pointing at.",
      "checksum": "sha256:05efe09067b98e8946ebc9d83505b2477ba943f4243428152edd14914e9643ed",
      "wav": "chunk-50.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 597
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "text": "Token capacity is not the only cost. A third commenter.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9570a156c7d034c4b785118e791b0376689c0fea28fcfd2aa321817e2c46b09f",
      "wav": "chunk-51.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 607
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "text": "A I tends to become significantly less accurate when you exceed ten to twenty percent of the maximum token capacity.",
      "checksum": "sha256:238d46fdefbadfbbe292b6dca7e0fd745a002e8a8228980d557be3cc4529edbc",
      "wav": "chunk-52.wav",
      "duration": 6.873106575963718,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 617
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "text": "So using H T M L with more code comes with a tradeoff.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a4821d79ec2edaee084cefed426b9b198c87e28f570c2d5cb0a07a67093efe6d",
      "wav": "chunk-53.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 637
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "text": "In other words \u2014 even when the budget exists, spending it on layout instead of content has a quality cost.",
      "checksum": "sha256:62ea3c33a0cb2bdb251015de8fbcce6dc49d7a96ae3cd288bb908d9db8e443a4",
      "wav": "chunk-54.wav",
      "duration": 6.362267573696145,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 650
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "text": "The community is not buying the it-barely-registers framing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:906f3249268525849eb4462981410d888d17eae67f47fdda95fb0646e9c4cfc7",
      "wav": "chunk-55.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 670
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "text": "And then there are the workflows people have actually settled on.",
      "checksum": "sha256:691fff73dd177dfdfa90f3b4b73eefec0974ccfe49f338a3e203659b86da7d70",
      "wav": "chunk-56.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 678
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "text": "Six patterns showed up repeatedly across the replies.",
      "checksum": "sha256:285b16845b72db86302305d01eb84fab11231d37115165f12d1af6b18fa4848e",
      "wav": "chunk-57.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 689
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "text": "Pattern one. Markdown for agents only. H T M L for agents and humans.",
      "checksum": "sha256:260b6e7ba1f76232007bb34c9431494f28d4bbfc132ebb7f9d6bc098472fcfba",
      "wav": "chunk-58.wav",
      "duration": 5.758548752834467,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 697
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "text": "The exact framing from a builder running a content system.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3381116e564a22b11fb58d22f4d13f118325ee074aaa8a04040549ef8fcde99b",
      "wav": "chunk-59.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 711
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "text": "Reviewing ideas, drafts, and a whole workspace end-to-end in markdown is \u2014 terrible U X.",
      "checksum": "sha256:83144b0e027f940938a9f6cf3083ac3a66e38fd36adcc7a59a9bbb7477de6fcf",
      "wav": "chunk-60.wav",
      "duration": 6.2693877551020405,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 721
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "text": "So markdown stays as the agent layer. H T M L becomes the human review layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c34e4cd7fcddc5aee3e95f9418e66059b354cb9a27c293e3ed2f2f405192d77e",
      "wav": "chunk-61.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 736
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "text": "Pattern two. Data visualization in H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e8cbdb9de094af1670fcafcc046fd43d72fc09787bc982dcee5c96c1d2e46f23",
      "wav": "chunk-62.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 752
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "text": "Everything else in markdown. There is no comparison for data viz. But for hierarchical text, a clean markdown viewer is just as legible.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e69c7762565be09e77b7298b49fb03d7fe05e38d06fb98a75bce45ab1ea69cb8",
      "wav": "chunk-63.wav",
      "duration": 9.102222222222222,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 761
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "text": "And saves tokens. Pattern three. Markdown for input.",
      "checksum": "sha256:876efa6136f7c4d146828fe0054e2759025da10b9641746d527d78b79da861db",
      "wav": "chunk-64.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 784
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "text": "H T M L for output to the customer. As everything \u2014 it depends.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f845c3e0981c3ae237c7915ca34cda059982e07afeed21f9305ff5a3041fe0d7",
      "wav": "chunk-65.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 792
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "text": "H T M L is great for output to the customer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:44a0f8594e7c08bc1a9fd4e10432abebf1080939302c9e9d646b56c684d5b964",
      "wav": "chunk-66.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 806
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "text": "M D is better for input. You must understand where you will use it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4157a462a527a28164f99aa0dcc5e487ab0c08f81eaee57259108de1b0f89bf9",
      "wav": "chunk-67.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 817
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "text": "Pattern four. M D X. The Markdown-plus-React format.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e950803c86e3c1847df570d2503388dcd74c9fcced713154cdb0f0116d392a05",
      "wav": "chunk-68.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 831
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "text": "One commenter. H T M L is triple the size and harder to read and write.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c98e06306b80910cf7f18ce3ac3aab6fe751229e48edf3627e8774ef7c27dbf7",
      "wav": "chunk-69.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 839
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "text": "The solution is M D X. Markdown is small, fast, readable.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6304d011dc5075e0f38ea47787766a6272c871c7e6491060b08565c9ff47825c",
      "wav": "chunk-70.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 855
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "text": "M D X combines dynamic content and web components when needed.\n\nPattern five.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6a9b334e4d48b80c7d3cf17f41690c3ef0dfd4d4e8b8fef8d2e6195709a30593",
      "wav": "chunk-71.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 866
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "text": "Mermaid stays in markdown. You would think H T M L would win here.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b055caca6dd5160d90aa9614d95922bdd0c06ac02ecee7b4e05d2f845ed5e434",
      "wav": "chunk-72.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 879
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "text": "But a markdown viewer with Mermaid support is way better.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2383e161f84f3e73aa083b1bbbcf5bd668dd338b5200b9317d22671fa56eb5ca",
      "wav": "chunk-73.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 893
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "text": "I don't want an L L M coding a custom network diagram when I already have a clean, standard, token-efficient way to view them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:55cefb100269ec2c69ff78d79b488ef204980f82a729b52b4abb7e495b614ebf",
      "wav": "chunk-74.wav",
      "duration": 6.780226757369615,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 903
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "text": "Pattern six. The conspiracy take. The framing \u2014 someone earning money on token spending suggests we spend more tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3396d2d0a893f71a3dde10263d744b141ccdb7e9e83674bb116c7d00fcb8a185",
      "wav": "chunk-75.wav",
      "duration": 7.569705215419501,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 927
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "text": "This one showed up four separate times in the comments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1e74d527308734dfd1bed56bedd296ee18d748399c017edfb9dd6909e0c5065d",
      "wav": "chunk-76.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 946
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "text": "It is worth taking seriously, even if you do not agree.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dd011d469d092222a9efd15a0c00de25863dc71692ef4ee32cf7c4d4b6ad653c",
      "wav": "chunk-77.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 956
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "text": "So where does this leave anyone trying to make a call?",
      "checksum": "sha256:46f6f513d577b01ad8b378927ba029fb8b2891c097733e644e4a410406e2addd",
      "wav": "chunk-78.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 967
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "text": "The consensus that earned the most agreements across both videos is not pick-one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e20c678302ddca610ba782461e2e29ce9123612c697091e7843fd509e4166cea",
      "wav": "chunk-79.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 978
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "text": "It is a split. For agent-to-agent communication.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f7053745d2d79bba845b3ceb21f5081a5d3d77bcfca99d5762e9865829465528",
      "wav": "chunk-80.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 991
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "text": "Specs. Plans. Claude dot M D files. Sub-agent instructions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4f7e89fbd71d05061145bcf6c0ce6a11e86582d6c170fe70f4e66851282de685",
      "wav": "chunk-81.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 998
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "text": "The lingua franca stays markdown. Smaller.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d47c51dc7659b3e74d08686e2a6b231b1a9d88f3e3810854e226757b0b665a00",
      "wav": "chunk-82.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 1007
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "text": "Cheaper. Less brittle. For agent-to-human communication.",
      "checksum": "sha256:72e666ee04b66266991d0819b92e879fd31cf0a3824aa61d194065eb62ff4015",
      "wav": "chunk-83.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 1013
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "text": "Code review. Reports. Mockups. Dashboards.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ecd1865ce2f7bde0554f8e6b9df4e657b35ebc16116ec2f46545911f50c4b528",
      "wav": "chunk-84.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 1019
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "text": "Anything a real person is going to actually look at and click through \u2014 H T M L makes a stronger case.",
      "checksum": "sha256:86003719de7602fa8aaf9e95460f523a44ee5e9687d6c6cf1d07695c4be8f709",
      "wav": "chunk-85.wav",
      "duration": 7.523265306122449,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 1024
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "text": "The split is not a compromise. It is a workflow.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8ec724174e7180bae15cd29eda88291c7f0b204c163c009e60a23dfceddb0916",
      "wav": "chunk-86.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1046
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "text": "The thesis that holds across both camps.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a38ed2534e1c3e03c28746626ddf24ec99a441d7272ca836965dcec372d6ad69",
      "wav": "chunk-87.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1056
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "text": "Wherever a human looks, H T M L. Everywhere else, markdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9f9711ba93caf29569a97c4d581868ce45e61f283b20bad133d4521e6ba005b9",
      "wav": "chunk-88.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1063
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "text": "And one outlier insight worth flagging. From a reply that did not get the like-count it deserved.\n\nMultimodality, the argument goes, is a sycophancy multiplier.",
      "checksum": "sha256:011222df55166e9e8bdb2f5b1bd61b974b6ab9b2e22b8bb21488c50cca760290",
      "wav": "chunk-89.wav",
      "duration": 9.93814058956916,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 1074
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "text": "Look at the rosy prose. Built around what you love.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9617bce708872a063d885ade8144e8e9e69c076bd107d73f0b9a3c3d843ffeec",
      "wav": "chunk-90.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1099
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "text": "Recommendation in one breath. I do not want to be talked to that way.",
      "checksum": "sha256:91b1a6c98ffe9305efb1a0bcdaf34a6f9595ebceb3fbcd8cba5526d76bc17aad",
      "wav": "chunk-91.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 1109
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "text": "The argument \u2014 richer formats may make agents nicer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:feb9c3b8599361cffd743fc0edbef53142c9ffa2e5412e248901271474647dc2",
      "wav": "chunk-92.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1123
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "text": "And nicer is not always honest. That one is not in the documentation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:166f67bff29d45517c0afef05789fe0b770a562387a0e36808155c4474e74697",
      "wav": "chunk-93.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1132
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "text": "It is something to watch. So where does the debate actually stand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:714880e5f9396e665e59d5eb25b44fd2f4ed0696722c1c3416e9ea43e51b3836",
      "wav": "chunk-94.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 1145
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "text": "As of right now. Thariq, the original poster, doubled down four days ago.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5d7735d81f238ca2b5a224878ddc38642ebd3278fabdc2b765f1fae41107c0c4",
      "wav": "chunk-95.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1157
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "text": "H T M L continues to be undefeated.\n\nThe replies under that post are still split.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6e8339f4a3d74cee90a07b26c0744eb5bd3b6ab81888e48324423a21e6ff9f9b",
      "wav": "chunk-96.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 1170
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "text": "Still arguing. Still posting receipts. The Markdown camp has not moved. Tokens still cost what they cost.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2d3226cb1ada746c5eae4ae79c1d99ca49bdb60a680bbfb0d1496a41942b1125",
      "wav": "chunk-97.wav",
      "duration": 6.919546485260771,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 1186
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "text": "Simplicity is still a feature. Markdown still renders to H T M L when needed.\n\nThe H T M L camp has not moved either.",
      "checksum": "sha256:640bc9aa2d23641e55b71a3326798e654539ec6837c0e06ea2acb0e2663e6acc",
      "wav": "chunk-98.wav",
      "duration": 7.244625850340136,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 1203
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "text": "Their artifacts get opened. Their reviews get clicks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:096c14604738128f035368d695fd2d5e0931c982a3fc207da0a26e1cb0c4a403",
      "wav": "chunk-99.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1228
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "text": "Their plans land in workflows. What changed in the last week is that the conversation is no longer one engineer versus a thousand replies.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d75eb94f0bf2ec8022d0504e48f5130680d39422a0e48935de262267a54b7c0a",
      "wav": "chunk-100.wav",
      "duration": 9.47374149659864,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 1236
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "text": "It is a set of patterns the community is converging on.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ec6a424b919d0354e60321e5a6368589de16f46a28bd0beebbe1531227772956",
      "wav": "chunk-101.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1260
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "text": "Slowly. Out loud. In public. So \u2014 which side are you on?",
      "checksum": "sha256:8a1ae95e740bd7f32b3ece00d12bd38696f902c210586a9c21ec21bb244dd063",
      "wav": "chunk-102.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 1271
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "text": "Markdown for everything. H T M L for everything.",
      "checksum": "sha256:aebb1949ed5e65ba31f0f348c58c340bdaeeea4b1acb74c0611cdfbccf29e41d",
      "wav": "chunk-103.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1283
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "text": "Or the hybrid \u2014 markdown for the agent, H T M L for the human.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ba07c697188ccf12cfb590877381af1cdd6bb619fdca909bce7760112f283d5c",
      "wav": "chunk-104.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 1292
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "text": "Drop your pick below. If you missed the first video on the thesis itself, the link is in the description.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8b69539fe3d115ec13eb7a06e31b38eb7007dbe959a0ef06ffb9ce1c33d4adfa",
      "wav": "chunk-105.wav",
      "duration": 6.176507936507937,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 1307
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "text": "And if you want to learn more about A I, check out the dynamous dot A I community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:78a496825e21407cc57c48fc3f5123e9693a97210b1d579c87f18bf8eae48492",
      "wav": "chunk-106.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1327
    }
  ]
}